---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About"
  description="How RealJobScope curates practical, experience-based career stories."
>
  <section class="page-hero about-hero animate-rise">
    <p><strong>About RealJobScope</strong></p>
    <h1>A practical guide to what jobs are really like.</h1>
    <p>
      RealJobScope publishes structured, first-person stories so students and career switchers can compare
      real day-to-day work before committing to a path.
    </p>
    <div class="cta-row">
      <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/jobs">Explore stories</a>
      <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="/share">Share your experience</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="about-grid" aria-label="Mission and standards">
    <article class="panel mission">
      <h2>Why we built this</h2>
      <p>
        Most career pages describe titles and salary ranges, but leave out workflow, tradeoffs,
        stress points, and growth patterns. We built RealJobScope to close that gap with concrete,
        experience-based reporting.
      </p>
      <p>
        The goal is simple: help people make less blind decisions by seeing how work actually feels
        over time.
      </p>
    </article>

    <aside class="standards" aria-label="Editorial standards">
      <h2>Editorial standards</h2>
      <dl>
        <div>
          <dt>Useful over polished</dt>
          <dd>We prioritize specific workflows, tools, and responsibilities.</dd>
        </div>
        <div>
          <dt>Balanced perspective</dt>
          <dd>Every story should include both rewards and difficult parts of the role.</dd>
        </div>
        <div>
          <dt>Reader-first</dt>
          <dd>Advice must be actionable for students and career switchers.</dd>
        </div>
      </dl>
    </aside>
  </section>

  <section class="principles" aria-label="What every story should answer">
    <h2>What every approved story should answer</h2>
    <div class="principles-grid">
      <article>
        <h3>What does a normal week look like?</h3>
        <p>Deliverables, meetings, tools, and collaboration rhythm.</p>
      </article>
      <article>
        <h3>What makes this role rewarding?</h3>
        <p>The moments and outcomes that keep people in the field.</p>
      </article>
      <article>
        <h3>What should readers watch out for?</h3>
        <p>Hard parts, tradeoffs, and who may not be a strong fit.</p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="process" aria-label="How stories are published">
    <h2>How a story gets published</h2>
    <ol>
      <li>
        <span>01</span>
        <p>Contributor submits a structured story.</p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <span>02</span>
        <p>Staff checks quality, clarity, and trust signals.</p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <span>03</span>
        <p>Approved stories appear in Wall of Paths and Jobs.</p>
      </li>
    </ol>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .about-hero {
    max-width: 78ch;
  }

  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.6fr) minmax(0, 1fr);
    gap: 1.1rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .mission h2,
  .standards h2,
  .principles h2,
  .process h2 {
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.12;
  }

  .standards {
    padding: 0.8rem 0;
  }

  .standards dl {
    margin: 1rem 0 0;
    display: grid;
    gap: 0.95rem;
  }

  .standards dt {
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 0.2rem;
  }

  .standards dd {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
  }

  .principles {
    margin-top: 1.2rem;
    padding-top: 1.1rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
  }

  .principles-grid {
    margin-top: 0.8rem;
    display: grid;
    gap: 0.9rem;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
  }

  .principles-grid article {
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 12px;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.72);
    padding: 0.85rem;
  }

  .principles-grid h3 {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 1.02rem;
  }

  .principles-grid p {
    margin: 0.45rem 0 0;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
  }

  .process {
    margin-top: 1.35rem;
    padding: 1.1rem;
    border: 1px solid rgba(15, 42, 59, 0.14);
    border-radius: 12px;
    background: var(--bg-panel);
    box-shadow: var(--surface-shadow);
  }

  .process ol {
    margin: 0.95rem 0 0;
    padding: 0;
    list-style: none;
    display: grid;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
  }

  .process li {
    padding: 0.8rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 10px;
    background: #fff;
  }

  .process span {
    display: inline-flex;
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--brand-primary);
  }

  .process p {
    margin: 0.4rem 0 0;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
  }

  @media (max-width: 920px) {
    .about-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .principles-grid,
    .process ol {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
